## Component Styling

Ensure mobile first approach and that any component you are working on is responsive and looks good.

## Maintaining a Style System

Use design tokens in Tailwind config for consistent styling:

```js
// tailwind.config.ts
module.exports = {
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        primary: {
          DEFAULT: '#FF6B35', // Vedic orange
          light: '#FF8C61',
          dark: '#E54B15',
        },
        scripture: {
          DEFAULT: '#4A5568', // For scripture-specific UI
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Always reference these design tokens instead of hardcoding colors or styles:

```tsx
// ❌ Bad
<div className="bg-[#FF6B35]">...</div>

// ✅ Good
<div className="bg-primary">...</div>
```